{
  "doc_id": "7851",
  "text": "It is unknown whether being a migraineur is a risk factor for an RCVS. [CITATION_1] There is some overlap in respect of epidemiology (both are more common in female) and pharmacology (some anti-migraine medication might trigger RCVS), but the prevalence of migraine appears similar in the general population (12-15%) and in RCVS. [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] Further controlled studies would be necessary to clarify this. [CITATION_4] What could be the potential link between migraine, RCVS and CAD?",
